	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Plans",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "GetPlans",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/plans",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"plans"
							]
						},
						"description": "Catalogo publico de planes para la landing. Anonimo. Cada plan incluye supportedBillingCycles y pricesUsdByCycle (ej. {\"Monthly\": 49, \"Yearly\": 490}) para que la landing muestre precio mensual y anual sin calcularlo del lado del cliente."
					},
					"response": [],
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const plans = pm.response.json();\r",
									"if (Array.isArray(plans) && plans.length > 0) {\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('firstPlanCode', plans[0].code);\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('secondPlanCode', plans[1]?.code || plans[0].code);\r",
									"    console.log('Plans loaded:', plans.map(p => p.code).join(', '));\r",
									"}\r"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"packages": {},
								"requests": {}
							}
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Subscriptions",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "GetMySubscription",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/subscriptions/me",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"subscriptions",
								"me"
							]
						},
						"description": "Suscripcion del tenant: plan, limites, renovacion, estado."
					},
					"response": [],
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const s = pm.response.json();\r",
									"if (s && s.planCode) {\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('currentPlanCode', s.planCode);\r",
									"    pm.environment.set('subscriptionStatus', s.status);\r",
									"    console.log('Subscription:', s.planCode, s.status);\r",
									"}\r"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"packages": {},
								"requests": {}
							}
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "ActivateSubscription",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('status 204', () => pm.response.code === 204 || pm.expect.fail('Got ' + pm.response.code + ': ' + pm.response.text()));\r",
									"if (pm.response.code === 204) pm.environment.set('subscriptionStatus', 'Active');\r"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"packages": {},
								"requests": {}
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{UrlBase}}/subscriptions/activate",
							"host": [
								"{{UrlBase}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"subscriptions",
								"activate"
							]
						},
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"billingCycle\": \"Monthly\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"description": "Self-service (permiso: subscription.plan.change). Solo funciona si la suscripcion esta en Trialing — convierte a Active y dispara un cobro real via PaymentApp (mismo evento SubscriptionRenewalDueIntegrationEvent que usa el job de renovacion periodica). Requiere que el tenant ya tenga un metodo de pago adjunto en PaymentApp (ver coleccion PaymentApp > ProviderCustomers > AttachPaymentMethod) — si no, el cobro falla y la suscripcion queda PastDue con reintentos via DunningJob, igual que cualquier renovacion fallida. 204 en exito; correr GetMySubscription despues para confirmar status=Active. billingCycle es opcional (\"Monthly\"/\"Yearly\") — se manda junto con la activacion; si se omite o es null, mantiene el ciclo que ya tenia el trial. Sin prorrateo: el cobro se hace al precio completo del ciclo elegido."
					},
					"response": []
				},
